decks.notes: This deck focuses on using powerful Elemental creatures like Risen Reef and Omnath, Locus of Creation to quickly overwhelm your opponent with aggressive plays. It also includes a strong control element with cards like Force of Negation and Subtlety to disrupt your opponent's strategy. The inclusion of Leyline Binding and Solitude provides additional removal options to keep the board clear for your creatures to attack. The deck's mana base is carefully constructed to ensure consistency and power in every game.

The deck focuses on using cards like Goryo's Vengeance and Ephemerate to cheat out powerful creatures like Atraxa, Grand Unifier and Ulamog, the Defiler from the graveyard for a quick win. Thoughtseize and Force of Negation help protect the combo pieces while Leyline Binding and Tainted Indulgence provide control elements. The strategy revolves around quickly filling up the graveyard with key creatures and then reanimating them at instant speed for a surprise attack, catching opponents off guard and overwhelming them for a swift victory.
